h1. widget

h2. Purpose

Changes scaffolding widget.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
description(widget:'textarea')
{code}

h2. Description

Changes scaffold tag to @<g:textArea ... />@

widget is also added to scaffolding tags for boolean(checkbox), date(datePicker), and *select tags, but those tags don't do anything with it. 

Error Code: This constraint only impacts look and does not create errors. 

